│ <badref> = add i8 %1, %y\n```\n\nThis confirms that `InstCombine`'s logic for `sub`        │
│ invokes the `Negator` to transform `Y - X` into `Y + (-X)`. The `Negator` then incorrectly │
│ sinks the negation into the `select` operand without considering the `nsw` flag.\n\n### 3. │
